{"title":"吃饭不要钱","authors":["徐迟"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饭不要钱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐迟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饭不要钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几曾听说过？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饭不要钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里看见过？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自古所没有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界也从无。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪能有这事？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕是说梦话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饭不要钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知是真的！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在咱公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菜蔬也免费。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说来不相信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭菜进了肚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起从前事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不觉心酸苦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前生活难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天做苦工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿顿吃不饱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛马都不如。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士流鲜血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇出胜利花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食庆丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办起大公社。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产翻几番，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食吃不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饭不要钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦想要实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消息传出去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界要震动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方一片红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁毛泽东。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}